author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: The DE25-Nano is a compact development and education platform based on Intel’s Agilex 5 SoC FPGA. It follows the format of the earlier DE10-Nano board but introduces a new architecture with expanded logic resources, upgraded memory, and updated processor support. title: DE25-Nano with 138K-LE Agilex 5 FPGA and Dual-Cluster ARM HPS
